title: Chippa Wilson - Create Your Vision - The Single Fin
description:
Arnette team athlete Chippa Wilson talks shaping single fins and surfs some local California swell near Newport Beach. 

Arnette Eyewear is the lens through which artists create their vision. Chippa wears the Witch Doctor, find yours at http://www.arnette.com
